She lookes and sees Etchingar. "Oh, Hello there.  Well, it you would 
like to join in on this you may.  We are trying to come up with plans 
to take over a ship. Any ideas? I figure if we can come up with a 
good plan, take over the ship, then we can hand it over to Magatron.  
He'd be pleased and we can all go back to Cybertron."
